dging by the actual votes, it seems true.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom=
: 5px;">Therefore it would be kind of=C2=A0<em>bad=C2=A0</em>for the court =
to declare the APE structure illegal: It=E2=80=99s a mess, it=E2=80=99s har=
