 holders were originally promised.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And then AMC and the suing shareholders went t=
o the Delaware judge and asked her lift the =E2=80=9Cstatus quo order=E2=80=
=9D=C2=A0and let this all happen, and on Wednesday <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31118652.257452/aHR0cHM6Ly9jb3VydHMuZGVsYX=
